reviewText: I am glad technologly allows us to continue to enjoy past entertainment. My family watched the Milton Berle TV shows so this provides many warm memories. I am glad it includes an Elvis Presley performance.

I purchased it for the Elvis Presley episode, but the DVD packaging gives no description on which Milton Berle episode that Elvis appeared on. Turns out it's the San Diego navy ship episode, NOT the Milton Berle episode filmed in New York. I'm still looking for that episode if anyone knows where to find it.
this dvd is remastered to keep best image of this tv show and memories of the begining of television
